e companies and Vietnamese engineers.\r\n\r\nTherefore, we gathered young engineers who deeply understood the language and culture of both Japan and Vietnam, and set up a new team in 2018. Beyond barriers such as geography and culture between the two countries, we would like to develop high-efficiency software by making the most of the strengths of both countries, and create new value together with our customers.\r\n\r\nThat\'s nothing but \"Rikai Technology\". \"R Rikai\" is a \"understanding\" in Japanese. It will grow more and more as a global software development company that understands Japanese companies and Vietnamese engineers, and will continue to be indispensable for both Japanese companies and Vietnamese engineers.'),(1717,330,'_description_intro','field_628126c34bd1b'),(1718,330,'bg_intro','340'),(1719,330,'_bg_intro','field_628126c24bd1a'),(1720,330,'dp_ss6','1'),(1721,330,'_dp_ss6','field_62812df700c9b'),(1722,346,'_wp_attached_file','2022/05/img-pro-ss5.png'),(1723,346,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1016;s:6:\"height\";i:777;s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"2022/05/img-pro-ss5.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"img-pro-ss5-300x229.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:229;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"img-pro-ss5-768x587.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:587;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(1724,330,'dp_ss5','1'),(1725,330,'_dp_ss5','field_62812e3967885'),(1726,330,'img_ss5','346'),(1727,330,'_img_ss5','field_62812e49a20c4'),(1728,354,'_wp_attached_file','2022/05/bg-pro-ss4.jpg'),(1729,354,'_w