tomers are small and medium-sized enterprises, start-up</li>\r\n 	<li>stage 2: \"Organic Growth Stage\" ・ Aim to reach 2,000 employees in the five years after the end of the first stage. Customers are major companies Stage</li>\r\n 	<li>3: \"Expansion Stage\" ・ Expand the market to the EU, US and South Korea.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPromote \"business centered on people and technology\" to the first stage for new markets with new goals . And the expansion of \"human organization\". Rikai Technology will continue to grow steadily, speedily and sustainably.'),(1735,330,'_excerpt_ss4','field_628130af4bd30'),(1736,330,'bg_ss4','354'),(1737,330,'_bg_ss4','field_628130b14bd31'),(1738,363,'_wp_attached_file','2022/05/number-05.png'),(1739,363,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:49;s:6:\"height\";i:30;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2022/05/number-05.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:0:{}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(1740,330,'dp_ss3','1'),(1741,330,'_dp_ss3','field_6281393b9b6cd'),(1742,330,'tt_ss3','Action'),(1743,330,'_tt_ss3','field_628139459b6ce'),(1744,330,'text_blur_ss3','Action'),(1745,330,'_text_blur_ss3','field_6281394e9b6cf'),(1746,330,'list_ss3_0_icon','274'),(1747,330,'_list_ss3_0_icon','field_6281397202b83'),(1748,330,'list_ss3_0_title','To trust'),(1749,330,'_list_ss3_0_title','field_6281397202b84'),(1750,330,'list_ss3_0_description','We always trust ourselves and our\r\norganization'),(1751,330,'_list_ss3_0_description','field_6281397202b85'),(1752,330,'list_ss3_1_icon','275'),(1753,330,'_list_ss3_1_icon','field_6281397202b83'),(1754,330,'list_ss3_1_title','Take pride'),(1755,330,'_list_ss3_1_title','field_6281397202b84'),(1756,330,'list_ss3_1_descripti