,'field_628317eb91761'),(2263,560,'_wp_attached_file','2022/05/img-new-ss3.png'),(2264,560,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:408;s:6:\"height\";i:387;s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"2022/05/img-new-ss3.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"img-new-ss3-300x285.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:285;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(2265,481,'tt_ss3','A new type of offshore development company'),(2266,481,'_tt_ss3','field_62831da0e2b2a'),(2267,481,'content_ss3_excerpt','We at Rikai are a new type of offshore development company that is different from either of them. It is an offshore development company created by a foreigner (Vietnamese) and headquartered in Japan, and it is a major feature that Japanese customers and foreign (Vietnamese) employees can have a win-win relationship. ..'),(2268,481,'_content_ss3_excerpt','field_62831dcbe2b2c'),(2269,481,'content_ss3_img','560'),(2270,481,'_content_ss3_img','field_628317eb83766'),(2271,481,'content_ss3_list_0_text','At Rikai, we will have excellent Vietnamese engineers who have a long history of living in Japan and who understand Japanese culture and business customs. And through close communication, we understand the intentions and intentions of the company in charge in detail. Instruct and manage the offshore development team on behalf of the company in charge. Our head office is in Japan, but our wage system is based on Vietnam, so our strength is that we can set low development costs.'),(2272,481,'_content_ss3_list_0_text','field_628317eb9994e'),(2273,481,'content_ss3_list_1_text','Rikai was founded in 2018, so it\'s not very well known yet. However, Doan Hai Bang, who was in charge of the Japanese subsidiary for more than 10 years at a major offshore development company headquartered in Vietnam and eventually led 1,300 engineers as the head of the business headquarters, said, \"Win-Win Offshore &lt;Win. -Win Offshore&gt; ”was established by our company to realize a new business model.'),(2274,481,'_content_ss3_list_1_text','field_628317eb9994e'),(2275,481,'content_ss3_list_2_text','As a \"Win-Win offshore\" only company, we are for \"customers who regard offshore development companies as strategic partners\" and \"customers who want to carry out long-term offshore development with high satisfaction\". We provide reliable technology and services.'),(2276,481,'_content_ss3_list_2_text','field_628317eb9994e'),(2277,481,'content_ss3_list','3'),(2278,481,'_content_ss3_list','field_628317eb83769'),(2279,481,'content_ss3',''),(2280,481,'_content_ss3','field_62831dbde2b2b'),(2283,563,'_wp_attached_file','2022/05/bg-ss3-wws.jpg'),(2284,563,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1440;s:6:\"height\";i:1142;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2022/05/bg-ss3-wws.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"bg-ss3-wws-300x238.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:238;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"bg-ss3-wws-1024x812.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:812;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"bg-ss3-wws-768x609.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:609;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(2285,481,'bg_ss3','563'),(22