velopment costs tend to be higher than onshore development, which has its headquarters in a foreign country. In addition, when it comes to developers of local employees, it is also true that there are issues such as \"no career path,\" \"high turnover rate,\" and \"low motivation.\"'),(5945,790,'_list_ss2_0_description','field_628317eb91761'),(5946,790,'list_ss2_1_image','677'),(5947,790,'_list_ss2_1_image','field_628317eb91759'),(5948,790,'list_ss2_1_title','Type 2'),(5949,790,'_list_ss2_1_title','field_628317eb9175e'),(5950,790,'list_ss2_1_description','\"A foreign-made offshore development company with a foreign headquarters\"\r\nDevelopment costs are very low. On the other hand, although Japanese is fluent, it takes time to communicate, anxiety due to the lack of a person in charge, and distrust due to lack of understanding of Japanese culture and business customs increase. However, when it comes to developers of local employees, there are merits such as \"having a career path,\" \"low turnover rate,\" and \"high motivation.\" For this reason, it can be said that this type of offshore development company has a strong meaning of \"Employee First\".'),(5951,790,'_list_ss2_1_description','field_628317eb91761'),(5952,790,'tt_ss3','A new type of offshore development company'),(5953,790,'_tt_ss3','field_62831da0e2b2a'),(5954,790,'content_ss3_excerpt','We at Rikai are a new type of offshore development company that is different from either of them. It is an offshore development company created by a foreigner (Vietnamese) and headquartered in Japan, and it is a major feature that Japanese customers and foreign (Vietnamese) employees can have a win-win relationship. ..'),(5955,790,'_content_ss3_excerpt','field_62831dcbe2b2c'),(5956,790,'content_ss3_img','560'),(5957,790,'_content_ss3_img','field_628317eb83766'),(5958,790,'content_ss3_list_0_text','At Rikai, we will have excellent Vietnamese engineers who have a long history of living in Japan and who understand Japanese 